{"tid":1500320,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"用音樂傳遞信念 讓繁花繼續盛放 - 27/8 繁花音樂祭","createTime":"2019-08-24T03:53:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T12:17:44.000Z","uid":31788,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"66fcdf956c7edbe60fd8ada9aa9d9d308ff1f71e","tid":1500320,"uid":31788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:53:41.000Z","msg":"【用音樂傳遞信念 讓繁花繼續盛放 - 27/8 繁花音樂祭】<br />\n<br />\n香港人的歷史時刻，每日都在上演。由過往一直互相指罵、劃清界線，到此刻終於無分你我成就真正的「We Connect」，為的就是自由的信念，能夠永久流傳，繼續繁衍。各界人士因為這場運動，被噤聲、殘害、解僱或被捕而剝奪寶貴的人生。<br />\n<br />\n面對眼前社會各界都奮起向受害人士伸出援手，TTN和Zuk的主理人雖算不上是高瞻遠矚的社會賢達，但感覺可以在自己的本位出一分力，幫助被捕義士早日回家或歸隊，抵抗白色恐佈。<br />\n<br />\n因此我們發起這場「繁花音樂祭」，借助獨立音樂界各位藝人和的幕後製作人的力量，為星火同盟籌款，門票收入將會不扣除任何成本下，全數捐出。<br />\n<br />\n時間實在倉促，但既然要做，就做得好好睇睇。<br />\n8月27日星期二晚，旺角麥花臣場館，不見不散。<br />\n<br />\nTTN x Zuk 繁花音樂祭 Summer Blossom Festival<br />\n日期：27/08/2019 TUE 星期二<br />\n時間：6-11PM<br />\n地點：旺角麥花臣場館<br />\n票價：$200或以上自由捐獻 (不設劃位 Free Standing &amp; Seating)<br />\n<br />\n購票：<br />\n<a href=\"http://tickcats.co/ticket/summerblossom/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftickcats.co%2Fticket%2Fsummerblossom%2F&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLqnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=561eb97a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tickcats.co/ticket/summerblossom/</a><br />\n<br />\n演出嘉賓（不按出場序；持續更新）：<br />\nSugar Bro<br />\n及時雨<br />\nCopak<br />\nAfter 10<br />\nPhoon<br />\nKolor<br />\nTeenage Riot<br />\nLuna Is A Bep<br />\nFeari^<br />\n(And more....)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://tickcats.co/ticket/summerblossom/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftickcats.co%2Fticket%2Fsummerblossom%2F&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLqnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=561eb97a\" target=\"_blank\">http://tickcats.co/ticket/summerblossom/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GgnMUFR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGgnMUFR.jpg&h=3b431d2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04a087f97ffd388cca4fd4e0e78f26b5221408f6","tid":1500320,"uid":31788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:27:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8658fc1348c02dd2d5fb69f1ccdb1bc0ab76066d","tid":1500320,"uid":265027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T07:12:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a39adabeca175ea0ae5db43837ccafd68aa9e904","tid":1500320,"uid":132478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:53:53.000Z","msg":"有冇人去緊"},{"pid":"1d36cc1de0f0b62678be0cd5333c0291020bcfe8","tid":1500320,"uid":51467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a39adabeca175ea0ae5db43837ccafd68aa9e904","tid":1500320,"uid":132478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:53:53.000Z","msg":"有冇人去緊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T11:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513276ed25ae8722793cd48449743433b84313a7","tid":1500320,"uid":117722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T12:17:44.000Z","msg":"買多左張，有興趣留tg"}]}